<% provide(:title, 'About Us') %>
<section class="wrapper aboutUs">
	
	<header class="row bottom_border">
		<h1>About Slinggit</h1>
	</header>
	
<div class="row">
	<article class="col3 pull_left">
		<p>Slinggit is built in sunny Denver, CO using the latest in space age materials. Our mission is to help people quickly find the things they want to buy and sell the things they don't.</p>
		<p>Our design and development philosophy is rooted in the belief that good user experience in software begins with speed. We work hard to maintain lightweight code and reduce the things, like images, that you need to load. This is even more true today than ever with the number of mobile devices and the immediacy you have to sell and buy things and get on with your life.</p>
	</article>
	
